import React from "react"; import {IProfile} from "../models/IProfile"; interface IProps { profile : IProfile } interface IState { } let GithubProfileDetails:React.FC =({profile}) =>{ return(
{profile.followers} Followers {profile.public_repos} Repos {profile.public_gists} Gists {profile.following} Following
  • NAME : {profile.name}
  • Location : {profile.location}
  • Email : {profile.email}
  • Company : {profile.company}
  • Blog : Blog
  • Member Since : {profile.created_at}
  • Profile URL : {profile.html_url}
) }; export default GithubProfileDetails;
